sources.style\\header.sass:
nav.header-menu a, div.header-buttons a
	text-decoration: none

a:active
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.75)



.header_style
	background-color: #FFFFFF
	width: 100%
	height: 70px
	box-shadow: 0px 10px 20px rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.05)
	display: flex
	align-items: center
	justify-content: space-between



.header-logo
	margin: 15px 0px 15px 90px



.header-menu
	min-width: 450px
	width: 527px
	display: flex
	justify-content: space-between
	margin: 26px 0 26px 300px
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-size: 14px
	line-height: 17px
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.5)

.header-menu__item_home
	font-weight: bold

.header-menu__item_services-icon
	padding-left: 3px



.header-buttons
	min-width: 180px
	width: 200px
	margin: auto auto auto 25px
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 12px
	line-height: 15px
	display: flex
	justify-content: space-between

.header-buttons__login
	padding: 9px 20px 10px 20px
	border: 2px solid #BC9CFF
	border-radius: 22px
	color: #BC9CFF
	
.header-buttons__register
	padding: 9px 20px 10px 20px
	border: 2px solid #BC9CFF
	border-radius: 22px
	color: #FFFFFF
	background: linear-gradient(180deg, #BC9CFF 0%, #8BA4F9 100%)

sources.style\\about.sass:
.about_style
    background: #FFFFFF
    box-shadow: 0px 1px 0px rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.1)
    display: flex
    align-items: center
    justify-content: space-around
    height: 372px

.logo_style
    width: 260px
    height: 156px
    display: flex
    align-content: space-between
    justify-content: flex-start
    flex-direction: column
    font-family: Montserrat
    font-style: normal
    font-weight: normal
    font-size: 14px
    line-height: 24px
    color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.75)


.about-menu
	width: 513px
	display: flex
	align-content: flex-start
	justify-content: space-between
	height: 170px

.about-links
	display: flex
	flex-flow: column nowrap
	justify-content: flex-start
	align-items: flex-start


.about-links a,span
	text-decoration: none
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-size: 14px
	line-height: 40px
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.5)

.about-links__header
	font-size: 12px
	font-weight: bolder
	text-transform: uppercase
	color: #1F2041
